snippet.title: Le Fetiche Maya gameplay (PC Game, 1989)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Le Fetiche Maya, Dos PC game produced by Silmarils in 1989 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/le-fetiche-maya/5192/
It is an exploration game where you have to find different things to pick.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
